    "body": "Sorry, missed the other questions. \r\n\r\n> Fatal: Error starting protocol stack: database version is v6, Geth 1.8.27-stable only supports v3\r\n\r\nYes, you have used the `1.9` (latest master) to create the database, and then tried to go back to `1.8.xx`. We're doing a version upgrade, so they're not compatible, and you cannot go back from 1.9 to 1.8. \r\n \r\nRegarding the clique error, have the two signers found eachother? How is the clique authorization round configured? \r\nPlease open a separate ticket for separate errors, instead of continuing on ths (closed) ticket\r\n",
